Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:38.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji parted ways with the Straw Hats\Nafter the duel against Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He thought he was determined but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he found himself leaving \Nthe Whole Cake Chateau.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afterwards, Luffy and Sanji saw each \Nother again at the rendezvous point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you {\i1}really{\i0} want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go back to the Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get the courage to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the wedding begins, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't stop anything by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those scum as my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna save their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got us! Let's crash the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Sanji Comes Back!\NCrash! The Tea Party from Hell!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:20.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,OUTSKIRTS OF SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei came to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. So Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} is okay too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the problem is\Nhow we join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they hear you're coming back,\NI'm sure they'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry - we should never have done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:05:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too ashamed to see Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others care about you\Nmore than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I scared her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the rain is stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:41.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,MIRRO-WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?! Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they can hear us\Nthrough this piece of glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror I was talking \Nthrough the last time we spoke
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:06:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,broke on the tree monster Kingbaum's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think there is at least a piece of glass\Nthat connects to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you there, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that...?\N--It's Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me if you're there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy! Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It's a piece of glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is his voice coming from a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story but\Nthey're in a mirror dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror dimension? Chopper and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Luffy! Great! You're really there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Is Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0} there too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!\NSo you got to see him again, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'm glad that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved everybody from \Ninside the mirror, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook even got a copy of the Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm impressed with you guys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:08:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your compliment doesn't make me happy,\Nyou fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You silly little goose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, it's good that Sanji's there\Nbut did you guys come to an agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji is not coming back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party\Nand the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Sanji's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sanji'll be back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! She's the Emperor of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want risk everyone's...\NI mean, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s life over a personal issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you and Luffy got into a big fight\Nso I was worried, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved! Really, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, then Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0} will \Ncome back to us, right, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For terrifying me like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's forget about it for now.\NThere isn't much time left before the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna get you back no matter what,\NSanji-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is it a proposal, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:50.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why but I feel as ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Luffy, we know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Sanji's sister saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanna save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, let's save them all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not aiming to\Ntake Big Mom down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she always looks forward to\Nthose tea parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By crashing it,\Nwe'll unleash the Emperor's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I think you guys have already faced\Nvarious Ministers on the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are just the tip of the iceberg\Nof the Big Mom Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even tougher ones will attend the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And underground rulers\Nfrom around the world are invited too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side, there are only...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ten of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fudge it!\NThere are only eight of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you all get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told everyone down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I need to share something\Nthat sounds slightly unrelated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:13:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Minister has arrived! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:14:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:06.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THIRD SON OF CHARLOTTE\N (MINISTER OF BEANS)\NBIG MOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:14.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE DAIFUKU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for Mama's tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BIG MOM'S TEA PARTY STARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's tea party starts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:43.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FIVE HOURS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in five hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the one who took Sanji away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the Worst Generation\Nwith a name as infamous as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the West Blue where he comes from,\Nfive powerful mafia families...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...rule their underground society.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five Families of the West -\None of the bosses of the five...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was "Gang" Bege.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His nickname "Gang" traces \Nback to his younger days
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\when he became notorious as a hit-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hit-man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was a sick young man\Nwho liked to hurt helpless living things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and watch them get weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did the same to crime families.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it were more bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lead tastes bitter, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he became a young mobster,\Nhe always aimed to kill bosses of the underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after he got his own family,\Nhe only killed his rival bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you betraying me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're outnumbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bege...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...never showed interest in \Nhis enemy's post or territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just took money and goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLOODY TRAGEDY! AN INTERNAL FEUD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAKING NIGHTMARE! UNDERGROUND REMAINS TENSE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE UNDERGROUND SOCIETY IN CHAOS\NTRIGGERED BY THE ASSASSINATION?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards he enjoyed watching\Nbloody tugs-of-war within groups
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how it upset the leaders\Nthat were secretly connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is really a disgusting man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he had such history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you hit someone,\Nyou'll get hit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He began to be targeted constantly\Nby those seeking vengeance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege even enjoyed that.\NHe built an impregnable castle and fought back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then mocked his enemy's disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An impregnable castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess he still hasn't \Nshown all of his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he got bored with life on land\Nand sailed out to sea, he did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became infamous for targeting only the captains of\Nwell-known pirate groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone still targeted on the sea\Nby enemies seeking revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being under the wing of the Emperor of the Sea\Nis the perfect safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he decided to affiliate with Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate how you work every day\Nso for the next tea party,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to put you in charge of security.\NDon't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom thought highly of his finely \Nhoned alertness and defensive capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he took the title of a "Rook" soldier\Nfor the upcoming tea party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has been entrusted with\Nfull authority over its security.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling us this now, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If security guards are on our side,\Nnothing can stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main event of the tea \Nparty is the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, Big Mom intends to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kill all the members of the \NVinsmokes at the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and acquire all of Germa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege is going to kill Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NSeems like everyone has their own plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, Pekoms who guided you guys to this island\Nwas actually taken by Bege and his clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was approached to \Ncooperate with their plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms... So that's what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate Mama too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Pekoms is a very loyal man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege let him fall into shark-filled \Nwaters to keep him quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my friends saw that\Nand saved him in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. So he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Bege, I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, here comes my main point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came up with a plan\Nafter I learned everything from Pekoms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I asked myself "What would you guys do?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was sure when you \Nlearned the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would say you want to \Nsave Sanji and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Pekoms\Nbut under the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}do you really want to\Nmake an enemy of Bege?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tea party starts at 10 in the morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About five hours from now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the ten of us\Nwho don't even have a plan yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brutes!\NI'll let them know what you are up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Luffy,\NBege's group is fully prepared for today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:30.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW HOURS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A few hours later,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy, one of the Worst Generation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Capone "Gang" Bege.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:55.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between these two pirates,\Nan unprecedented operation is hatched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:12.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Changing into a new outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:16.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others prepare\Nfor the impending tea party!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:19.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two rogues from the East and the West!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Bege are incompatible \Nwith each other!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a tense atmosphere,\Na forbidden meeting now begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Secret Meeting! Luffy \Nvs. the Fire Tank Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
